## DiaFoot.AI v2 \'97 Cascaded Computer Vision System for Diabetic Foot Ulcer Triage and Segmentation\
\
**Student:** Ruthvik Bandari  \
**Course:** AAI6620 Computer Vision  \
**Date:** March 2026\
